Defendant Danny J Keys in court with attorney Michael L. Chernin.  Kristi J Gordon appeared for the State of Wisconsin.  Amended information filed.  Defendant pleads guilty to the amended counts 1 and 2.  Court finds the defendant guilty of counts 1 and 2.  State makes recommendations.  Attorney Chernin makes statements.  Defendant makes statements.  

The Court Orders the Following:  Count 1
Imposed and Stayed Sentence of: 
100 Days Huber with STANDARD RELEASE CONDITIONS.  (Credit -0 days).  Concurrent. 
Term of Probation: 1 Year may be transferred to Milwaukee
Conditions of Probation:
Follow through with any treatment and/or counseling recommended by Agent;
AODA Assessment and follow through with any treatment recommended;
Absolute Sobriety; Random U.A.s;
No Use or Possession of illegal controlled substances or drug paraphernalia;
Not to use or posses any firearms	
Sign Medical Release for Agent;
Continue employment;
Condition Time: 5 days Huber with  NON WORKING HOURS WITH STANDARD RELEASE CONDITIONS - consecutive,  STAYED to be used at the Agents discretion
FINE: $505.00 to be paid as a condition of probation

